 .", "bbox": [268.9, 753.1, 822.2, 773.9]}, {"text": "35", "bbox": [889.9, 753.1, 910.8, 773.9]}, {"text": "26", "bbox": [986.9, 753.1, 1007.7, 773.9]}, {"text": "24", "bbox": [1073.4, 753.1, 1094.2, 773.9]}, {"text": "Net Sales Mix:", "bbox": [143.8, 786.4, 269.0, 807.3]}, {"text": "North America . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 811.4, 822.2, 832.3]}, {"text": "55%", "bbox": [889.9, 811.4, 928.1, 832.3]}, {"text": "55%", "bbox": [986.9, 811.4, 1025.1, 832.3]}, {"text": "55%", "bbox": [1073.4, 811.4, 1111.6, 832.3]}, {"text": "International . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [227.2, 836.4, 822.2, 857.3]}, {"text": "45", "bbox": [889.9, 836.4, 910.8, 857.3]}, {"text": "45", "bbox": [986.9, 836.4, 1007.7, 857.3]}, {"text": "45", "bbox": [1073.4, 836.4, 1094.2, 857.3]}, {"text": "Consolidated . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [268.9, 869.8, 822.2, 890.6]}, {"text": "100%", "bbox": [879.5, 869.8, 928.1, 890.6]}, {"text": "100%", "bbox": [976.4, 869.8, 1025.1, 890.6]}, {"text": "100%", "bbox": [1062.9, 869.8, 1111.6, 890.6]}, {"text": "Revenue increased 39% in 2007, reflecting revenue growth in both our North America and International", "bbox": [185.5, 932.3, 1055.3, 953.1]}, {"text": "segments. Additionally, changes in currency exchange rates positively affected net sales by $399 million for", "bbox": [143.8, 957.3, 1048.5, 978.2]}, {"text": "2007. For a discussion of the effect on revenue growth of exchange rates, see “Effect of Exchange Rates” below.", "bbox": [143.8, 982.3, 1085.6, 1003.2]}, {"text": "The North America revenue growth rate was 38% in 2007. This revenue growth primarily reflects increased", "bbox": [185.5, 1032.3, 1087.3, 1053.2]}, {"text": "unit sales driven largely by our continued efforts to reduce prices for our customers, including from our free", "bbox": [143.8, 1057.3, 1046.2, 1078.2]}, {"text": "shipping offers and Amazon Prime, a larger base of sales in faster growing categories such as electronics and", "bbox": [143.8, 1082.4, 1055.4, 1103.2]}, {"text": "other general merchandise, increased in-stock inventory availability, and increased selection of product offerings.", "bbox": [143.8, 1107.4, 1092.0, 1128.2]}, {"text": "The International revenue growth rate was 39% in 2007. This revenue growth reflects increased unit sales", "bbox": [185.5, 1157.4, 1069.0, 1178.2]}, {"text": "driven largely by our continued efforts to reduce prices for our customers, including from our free shipping", "bbox": [143.8, 1182.4, 1039.8, 1203.2]}, {"text": "offers, a larger base of sales in faster growing categories such as electronics and other general merchandise,", "bbox": [143.8, 1207.4, 1042.6, 1228.2]}, {"text": "increased in-stock inventory availability, and increased selection of product offerings. Additionally, changes in", "bbox": [143.8, 1232.4, 1071.2, 1253.2]}, {"text": "currency exchange rates positively affected International net sales by $390 million in 2007.", "bbox": [143.8, 1257.4, 906.5, 1278.2]}, {"text": "We expect that, over time, our International segment will represent 50% or more of our consolidated net", "bbox": [185.5, 1307.4, 1056.6, 1328.3]}, {"text": "sales. Additionally, as we continue to offer increased selection, lower prices, and additional product lines within", "bbox": [143.8, 1332.4, 1080.4, 1353.3]}, {"text": "our electronics and other general merchandise category, we expect to see the relative mix of sales from this", "bbox": [143.8, 1357.4, 1039.3, 1378.3]}, {"text": "category increase. See “Supplemental Information” below.", "bbox": [143.8, 1382.4, 634.9, 1403.3]}, {"text": "31", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}